item.title: About
item.description: I am a student currently studying Electronics Engineering, with a passion for cybersecurity and a thirst for tech stuff. This is my personal blog site, which I set up with a view to document my journey learning cybersecurity through articles on topics I learn. Besides the site will also hold some other tech stuff that I might be interested in and take up as a project. One basic point of this site will be CTFs.
